SPTSearchQueryType

Defines types of result objects that can be searched for.

typedef NS_ENUM(NSUInteger, SPTSearchQueryType ) {
   SPTQueryTypeTrack = 0,
   SPTQueryTypeArtist,
   SPTQueryTypeAlbum,
   SPTQueryTypePlaylist,
};
